title: Successful women-centred wellbeing project celebrated (Leeds Metropolitan University)
text: ( Source : Leeds Metropolitan University ) A successful pilot project to support the health and wellbeing of disadvantaged young women in the Halifax area is set to be celebrated at an event at Leeds Beckett University on Wednesday 4 November .
